headline: Tempus Achieves Record Total Contract Value Exceeding $1.1 Billion
summary: CHICAGO, January 11, 2026--Tempus AI, Inc. (NASDAQ: TEM), a technology company leading the adoption of AI to advance precision medicine, today announced a record Total Contract Value (TCV) of >$1.1 billion as of December 31, 2025. During 2025, Tempus signed data agreements with over 70 customers, spanning both large and mid-sized pharma, including AstraZeneca, GlaxoSmithKline, Bristol Myers Squibb, Pfizer, Novartis, Merck, Abbvie, Daiichi Sankyo, Eli Lilly, Boehringer Ingelheim, and biotechs inc
